snippet.title: Ezra Miller & Amber Heard | SHOULD THE DCEU / WB FIRE Or RECAST THEM?!
snippet.description:
As excited as we are for DC Fandome - the DCEU has certain controversies with certain actors - EZRA MILLER (The Flash) for choking a fan & the tarnished reputation of AMBER HEARD (Mera / Aquaman) amidst the Johnny Depp trial. Should they be fired or recast? Here are our thoughts!
#EzraMiller #AmberHeard #TheFlash
